

Keywords:
		Search keywords: 	SV VMM vmm_test vmm_unit

Technical content:
 
		Title: 		VMM_TEST , `vmm_test_begin, `vmm_test_end, test concatenation
 
		Objective:     Usage of `vmm_test_begin, `vmm_test_end macros and test concatenation.

		Description:   This test shows how to use macros for tests(please refer tests.sv).
		               +vmm_test=<> run-time option is used to select a specific test while running. 
																	
		Additional setup: None	
 
 To run the example:
      Using Makefile:
       	clean           -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
								run1            -- Run test1 (uses +vmm_test=test1)
								run2            -- Run test2 (uses +vmm_test=test2)
     Using shell scripts:
        clean.csh       -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
        comp.csh        -- To compile the design
        run.csh         -- To run the design  
 
 
Location Information:
		PATH: 			$VCS_HOME/doc/examples/testbench/sv/vmm/std_lib/vmm_simulation/vmm_test_macro
		DIAGRAMS: 		None

